- Professional color scheme
- Responsive grid system

### User Experience
- Clear navigation with breadcrumbs
- "Read More" buttons with visual indicators
- Back-to-home navigation on article pages
- Professional typography and spacing

## ğŸ”§ Development

### File Modifications

**To change the blog title:** Edit the header in `views/layout.ejs`

**To modify styles:** Edit `public/css/style.css`

**To add new routes:** Edit `routes/posts.js`

**To update article content:** Edit `data/posts.json`

